		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">22.1406</ph> Complaint procedures.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d1450e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1464e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Following agency procedures, the contracting office shall forward any complaints received about the administration of the Act to-</p>
					          <ol id="d1450e23" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1464e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Director, Office of Federal Contract Compliance Programs, U.S. Department of Labor, 200 Constitution Avenue, NW, Washington, DC 20210; or</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1464e36" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Any OFCCP regional or area office.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1464e47" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The OFCCP shall institute investigation of each complaint and shall be responsible for developing a complete case record.</p>
				        </li>
